race.comment: ARTGIRL (1) comes here with a distinct fitness edge over the bulk of these in a weaker contest. Slow into stride before attacking the line late with a respectable fourth over 1250m at this track. Expected to shed her Maiden status at start five. CAPDIVA (2) drops further in weight today after coming out of the same race as ARTGIRL, when third last start. Will roll forward and shapes as the main danger. RASKOL (10) away only fairly on debut before warming up late with an eye-catching third over 1000m at Gosford. Extra trip in her favour from the low gate. Genuine top-three prospect. IN LIMBO (16) resumes after failing to deliver when last in work. Has impressed in her two latest trials and looks set for a good campaign.
